spec_data.Name: perl-Test-Distribution
spec_data.Description:
When using this module in a test script, it goes through all the modules in
your distribution, checks their POD, checks that they compile OK and checks
that they all define a $VERSION.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 04:38:45 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Perform tests on all modules of a distribution
